titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on rosachloride lumps.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 4/1/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend the duty on 1 amino-2 chloro-4 hydroxy anthraquinone 9.10-anthracenedione, 1-amino-2-chloro-4-hydroxy (rosachloride lumps) through December 31, 1997.
